title: Introduction
body:
Hello Miss Dasiy, how are you this fine night?

[[I am very well! Thank you|VeryWell]]
[[I am not feeling well!|NotWell]]

title: VeryWell
body:
Oh that is truly lovely to hear! I hope I'll be seeing you again tonight?

[[Oh of course|Confirm]]
[[No, fuck off you creep|Fuckoff]]

title: NotWell
body:
Oh that is a shame to hear, I hope you will be well in the evening?

[[Oh I do think so, I will be more than fine|Confirm]]
[[Oh i am terribly afraid my frail southern constitution won't be able to attend|decline]]

title: Confirm
body: Oh lovely! I look forward to seeing you soon!

title: FuckOff
body: Oh how awfully rude of you!

title: decline
body: Oh that is a shame and most foul, but I am sure you will be well soon!
